main event: On 24 August 1961, a UFO sighting incident was documented near York, New York.
interesting points: The UFO was observed for a duration of 60 minutes,There was only one object reported,The analysis of photographs concluded that the objects were caused by poor photo processing,Several other photographs submitted were deemed inconclusive as they did not show clear unidentified objects,The sighting was investigated under Project Blue Book.
witness description: The witness information is not provided in the report.
